      "raw_bytes": "88 00 8D E6 95 05 21 04 03 00 02 00 CC CC CC CC CC CC CC CC CC CC",
      "notes": "Button packets store device ID as little-endian (reversed from printed label). To get display ID, read bytes [2-5] as little-endian. CRC omitted - will be computed.",
